Write a program that will create a moving average plot of the NASA global temperature anomaly data for a user specified moving average window. 

The user will specify a window size that should be an odd number of years. 

The program should calculate the required moving average for as many years in the data as possible and then create a plot of the annual data, shown with data symbols, and the moving average, shown as a solid line.



PROGRAM plot_temp_anomaly_moving_average
    Load anomaly data from TXT file
    Extract year column and annual temperature anomaly column
    Divide annual temperature anomalies by 100 for actual values
    Get minimum and maximum years possible for range

    WHILE true DO
        Get window size interval from user to calculate moving average

        Check if interval is an integer
        IF not integer THEN
            print "Please enter an integer."
            return to start
        ENDIF

        IF interval % 2 == 0 THEN
            // the input is even, restart
            print "Enter an odd year window size."
            return to start
        ENDIF

        IF interval < 2 THEN
            print "Enter a window size greater than 1."
            return to start
        ENDIF

        IF interval > (max year - min year) - 1 THEN
            print "Window size is too big. Please enter a smaller value."
            return to start
        ENDIF

        break
    ENDWHILE

    Calculate interval slice as integer division of interval by 2
    Calculate the first and last years for the moving average calculation
    Find the start and end indices for those years in the dataset

    Create empty arrays for the moving average years and moving average anomalies

    moving year index = 0
    FOR year index from start index to end index
        Obtain the subset of temperature anomalies surrounding the current year
        Calculate the mean of this anomaly subset
        
        Log the current year into the moving years array
        Log the calculated mean into the moving anomalies array
        
        Increase moving year index by 1
    ENDFOR

    Plot moving average anomalies against the moving years array
    Set X-axis label, Y-axis label, and Title
    Display the plot

ENDPROGRAM




